With Blazor Server and `MapBlazorHub` we used to support configuring various SignalR options (`HttpConnectionDispatcherOptions`) that it looks like we no longer expose anywhere when using interactive server rendering in a Blazor Web App:

```csharp
app.MapBlazorHub(options =>
{
    options.WebSockets.CloseTimeout = new TimeSpan(1, 1, 1);
    options.LongPolling.PollTimeout = new TimeSpan(1, 0, 0);
});
```

